          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>New Jersey Betting and Equal Treatment Act of 2015</b></p> <p> Amends the federal judicial code to exempt a lottery, sweepstakes, or other betting, gambling, or waging scheme operating exclusively in New Jersey, to the extent such scheme is approved by that state's legislature by statute, from the prohibition against a governmental entity, or a person acting pursuant to the law or compact of<em><strong> </strong></em>a governmental entity, sponsoring, operating, advertising, or promoting sports gambling.</p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2015-01-21T05:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
        </item>
